---
title: Kiwi Haloumi & Roast Pumpkin Toss with Herbed Mayo & Spring Onion
description: Who doesn’t like a bit of char on their haloumi? This one gets a generous coating of our punchy Kiwi spice blend before it crisps up in the pan until golden. Finish it off with a bed of roasted veggies (that'll take barely any effort to whip up) and top it off with a sprinkling of spring onion for an outstanding pairing of flavours – without the sweat and tears.

*We’ve replaced the crispy shallots in this recipe with spring onion due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
